A lightweight PHP MVC framework. This is a refactored version of code initially developed at <a href="http://technorati.com">Technorati</a> by Matthew Levine, Andrei Scheinkman and Ryan King with later development by Stephen Handley and Courtland Alves, who is currently leading the project. 

Please see an example implementation at http://github.com/temovico/temovico_example

here's a suggested http-conf:  

<VirtualHost *:80>
...
</VirtualHost>



